{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_义庄管事",
  "entry": "root_gate",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·义庄管事上门（半推半架）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "n_archive": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "addArchiveEntry",
          "params": {
            "bookType": "character",
            "entryId": "yizhuang_keeper"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "root"
    },
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_义庄镇尸",
              "state": "all_done",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "先生的大恩……庄里给你立个长生牌位！哦不不，呸呸，给你多包一份钱！",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "laugh"
      }
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "关、关先生！可算寻着你了！义庄……义庄出事了！！",
      "next": "n2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（压着嗓子，眼珠子直打颤）庄里停的两具死人子——在地上、扭着！揪着！互相压起！守夜的瞄了一眼，裤儿都吓湿了，人已经跑没影喽！",
      "next": "n3",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "……扭着？死人子还能自己下板凳？你娃莫是把酒当饭吃了迈。",
      "next": "n4",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "smirk"
      }
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "小的哪敢拿这种事开玩笑！正经先生……正经先生庄里请不起嘛。你是「李天狗那一脉」，你肯定有法子！钱！钱好说！",
      "next": "c1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "fear"
      }
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "ying",
          "text": "「……带路。」（钱好说这三个字，最管用）",
          "next": "c_go"
        },
        {
          "id": "tui",
          "text": "「老子今天不得空——」（话没说完就被拽住了袖子）",
          "next": "c_drag"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_drag": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "管事力气不大，架不住豁得出去——半求半拽，关二狗就这么被「请」上了路。",
      "next": "c_go"
    },
    "c_go": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "switchScene",
          "params": {
            "targetScene": "义庄",
            "targetSpawnPoint": "entry"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "beishi_busy": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "行内人做事有个先来后到。肩上这位先送进来，别的再讲。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "root_gate": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "next": "beishi_busy",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "plane": "背尸"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n_archive"
    }
  }
}
